# FlowCanvas Design System Rules

## Color Tokens (Tailwind classes only — NEVER hardcode hex)
These are the ONLY valid background/text/border colors:

### Canvas & App Shell
- Canvas bg: bg-[#0E0D0C] (the infinite canvas surface)
- App shell/sidebars: bg-surface-container (maps to #1f201e)
- Elevated panels: bg-surface-container-high (#2a2a29)
- Floating modals/command palette: bg-surface-container-highest (#353533)
- Lowest surface (darkest): bg-surface-container-lowest (#0e0e0d)

### Text
- Primary text: text-on-surface (#e5e2df)
- Secondary/muted: text-on-surface-variant (#bec8ca)
- Faint/metadata: text-outline (#899294)
- On-teal buttons: text-on-primary (#00363d)

### Accent (Teal)
- Primary teal: text-primary / bg-primary / border-primary (#8ad2de in dark mode)
- Teal bg tint: bg-primary/10
- Active teal border: border-primary (1px only)

### Status Colors
- In Progress: teal (primary)
- Blocked: amber → use text-[#E8AF34] and bg-[#E8AF34]/10
- Done: green → use text-[#6DAA45]
- In Review: purple → use text-[#A86FDF]
- Critical Path: gold → use text-[#E8AF34] with font-mono-label

### Project Accent Colors (assign one per project)
- Coral: #E05C5C
- Amber: #E8AF34
- Violet: #A86FDF
- Sky Blue: #5591C7
- Mint: #6DAA45

## Typography (STRICT — no deviations)
- Body copy: text-body-md (14px Geist) or text-body-sm (13px Geist)
- Section headers: text-section-header (11px, uppercase, tracked — Geist)
- Metadata/IDs/timestamps/effort: font-mono-label text-mono-label (12px JetBrains Mono)
- Headlines: text-headline-sm (18px Geist medium) — task panel titles only
- Large KPI numbers: text-display-lg (32px Geist semibold) — dashboard only
- NEVER use arbitrary font sizes. Only these 6 tokens.

## Spacing (4px grid — no arbitrary values)
- Use Tailwind spacing units that map to 4px multiples: p-1(4px), p-2(8px), p-3(12px), p-4(16px), p-6(24px), p-10(40px)
- Sidebar width: w-[260px] (fixed)
- Task detail panel width: w-[360px] (fixed)
- Top bar height: h-12 (48px)
- Compact row height: h-8 (32px)

## Component Rules
### Cards / Task Nodes
- NEVER use colored side borders (border-l-4 border-coral etc) — this is banned
- Use box-shadow glow for status instead: shadow-[0_0_0_1px_rgba(79,152,163,0.4)] for in-progress
- Top accent border (2px) is ALLOWED on canvas task nodes only: border-t-2
- Card bg: bg-surface-container-high with border border-white/[0.08]
- Card radius: rounded-xl (canvas nodes) or rounded-lg (panel lists)
- NO backdrop-filter blur on canvas nodes — causes ReactFlow perf issues at scale

### Buttons
- Primary: bg-primary text-on-primary rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-body-sm font-medium
- Ghost: border border-white/10 text-on-surface-variant hover:bg-white/5 rounded-lg
- Destructive: border border-[#DD6974]/40 text-[#DD6974] hover:bg-[#DD6974]/10 rounded-lg
- NEVER gradient buttons

### Status Dots
- 8px circle: w-2 h-2 rounded-full
- In Progress: bg-primary
- Blocked: bg-[#E8AF34] animate-pulse
- Done: bg-[#6DAA45]
- In Review: bg-[#A86FDF]
- Not Started: bg-outline

### Load Rings (SVG, not CSS border tricks)
- Use SVG <circle> with strokeDasharray for workload rings
- Green < 60%, Amber 60-80%, Red > 80% (animate-pulse on red)

### Borders
- Dividers: border-white/5 (very subtle)
- Panel borders: border-white/[0.08]
- Input focus: border-primary (replace border-white/10 on focus)
- NEVER solid gray borders — always white/opacity variants

## Dot Grid Pattern (Canvas Background)
```css
background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(205,204,202,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
background-size: 24px 24px;
```

## Banned Patterns (from Stitch audit)
- border-r-2 border-primary on sidebar nav items → replace with bg-primary/10 left pill
- backdrop-filter on canvas nodes → remove entirely
- Material Symbols font → replace all with Lucide icons
- inline style={{ color: '#...' }} → use Tailwind classes only
